msgid "# triton.language.reshape"
msgstr "# triton.language.reshape"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:2
msgid "## 1 功能作用说明"
msgstr "## 1 Function Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:4
msgid "将张量重新解释为新的形状。"
msgstr "Reinterpret the tensor as a new shape."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:6
msgid "**语法：**"
msgstr "**Syntax:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:8
msgid ""
"- `triton.language.reshape(input, shape, can_reorder=False)` - 函数调用形式\n"
"- `input.reshape(shape, can_reorder=False)` - 成员函数形式\n"
msgstr ""
"- `triton.language.reshape(input, shape, can_reorder=False)` - function call form\n"
"- `input.reshape(shape, can_reorder=False)` - member function form\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:10
msgid "**功能：**"
msgstr "**Function:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:12
msgid "- 将张量重新解释为新的形状"
msgstr "- Reinterpret the tensor as a new shape"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:14
msgid "## 2 参数规格"
msgstr "## 2 Parameter Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:16
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:18
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 必需 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| input | tensor | 是 | 输入张量 |\n"
"| shape | List[int] | 是 | 目标形状 |\n"
"| can_reorder | bool | 否 | 是否允许重新排序元素，默认False |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Required | Description |\n"
"|----------------|------|----------|-------------|\n"
"| input | tensor | Yes | Input tensor |\n"
"| shape | List[int] | Yes | Target shape |\n"
"| can_reorder | bool | No | Whether to allow reordering of elements, default False |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:20
msgid "**返回值：**"
msgstr "**Return value:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:22
msgid ""
"- **类型：** tensor\n"
"- **形状：** 与shape参数指定的目标形状相同\n"
"- **数据类型：** 与输入张量相同\n"
"- **内存布局：** 根据can_reorder参数决定\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Type:** tensor\n"
"- **Shape:** Same as the target shape specified by the shape parameter\n"
"- **Data type:** Same as the input tensor\n"
"- **Memory layout:** Determined by the can_reorder parameter\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:24
msgid "**约束条件：**"
msgstr "**Constraints:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:26
msgid ""
"- 输入和输出张量的总元素数必须相等\n"
"- 所有tensor不允许某个shape的size小于1\n"
msgstr ""
"- The total number of elements in the input and output tensors must be equal.\n"
"- For all tensors, the size of any shape dimension must not be less than 1.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:28
msgid "### 2.2 DataType支持表"
msgstr "### 2.2 DataType Support Table"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:30
msgid ""
"| 支持情况 | int8 | int16 | int32 | int64 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | float16 | float32 | bfloat16 | float8e4 | float8e5 | float64 | bool |\n"
"|----------|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:------:|:------:|:-------:|:----:|:----:|:------:|:---:|\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ |\n"
"| GPU支持 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Support Status | int8 | int16 | int32 | int64 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | float16 | float32 | bfloat16 | float8e4 | float8e5 | float64 | bool |\n"
"|----------|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:------:|:------:|:-------:|:----:|:----:|:------:|:---:|\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ |\n"
"| GPU Support | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:32
msgid "### 2.3 Shape支持表"
msgstr "### 2.3 Shape Support Table"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:34
msgid "支持任意维度数、任意形状大小。"
msgstr "Supports any number of dimensions and any shape size."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:36
msgid "### 2.4 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.4 Special Restrictions Explanation"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:38
msgid "* can_reorder参数仅支持False"
msgstr "* The `can_reorder` parameter only supports `False`"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:40
msgid "### 2.5 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.5 Usage"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/reshape.md:42
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"import torch\n"
"import triton\n"
"import triton.language as tl\n"
"\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def reshape_example(out_ptr):\n"
"    # 创建2x3x4的张量\n"
"    x = tl.zeros([2, 3, 4], dtype=tl.float32)\n"
"\n"
"    # reshape为6x4\n"
"    y = tl.reshape(x, [6, 4])\n"
"\n"
"    # 将结果写回外部张量\n"
"    offs = tl.arange(0, 6)[:, None] * 4 + tl.arange(0, 4)[None, :]\n"
"    tl.store(out_ptr + offs, y)\n"
"\n"
"## 调用示例\n"
"out = torch.empty((6, 4), dtype=torch.float32, device=\"npu\")\n"
"reshape_example[(1,)](out)\n"
"print(out.shape)  # 输出: torch.Size([6, 4])\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

